The connector uses **OAuth2 client_credentials grant** via Adobe IMS. On first use (or when the cached token expires), it POSTs to `https://ims-na1.adobelogin.com/ims/token/v3` with the client_id and client_secret to obtain a Bearer token. All subsequent Analytics API calls include:
```
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
x-api-key: {client_id}
Content-Type: application/json
```
